			<dd><div>The user takes the form of Primal Midgardsormr,<br>deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>inflicts stun, then returns to their original form.<br>The user then deals further damage to<br>surrounding enemies. This second attack<br>significantly reduces the mode gauge.<br>Certain abilities that activate while shapeshifting<br>will affect Primal Midgardsormr's attack.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 271 × 8 hits<br>Damage: 2,025 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,200<br>Special Effects:<br>・Stun<br>　　Lasts 6 seconds</div></dd></dl></div>
