<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5afbfed2a0695ef225275efc2ff0f1072.png"></span><span>Pounder of Mochi II</span></dt><dd><div>Grants the user a unique force strike that<br>reduces the strength of surrounding enemies<br>by 2% for 10 seconds, and will continue to<br>attack as long as your finger touches the<br>screen. In addition, every time this force strike<br>or the Splendid Spring skill hit enemies a total<br>of nine times, the user will be granted the<br>"Mochi Master" effect.<br>This force strike's strength reduction effect<br>can stack up to four times, and Mochi Master<br>can stack up to three times.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/42aad01fa9cb510052712a9ef6882f4b2.png"></span><span>Freeze Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to freezing by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b7917ce09425e1b4aaaa3eba8c9c70782.png"></span><span>Force Strike Attack Rate +20%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases force strike attack rate by 20%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Some skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.</div><div>・The adventurer Bondforged Prince&#39;s skills cannot be shared.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding Bondforged Prince&#39;s Standard Attacks and Skills<br>Abilities that increase damage dealt while shapeshifted (such as Dragon Damage +X%) and abilities that grant effects to attacks performed while shapeshifted (such as Windwyrm&#39;s Dragonlight) apply to the fifth attack in Bondforged Prince&#39;s standard attack combo and the attacks performed by Primal Midgardsormr when the skills Blazing Tempest and Vortex Circlet are used.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about the Platinum Showcase, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select the Platinum Showcase and check the Appearance Rates section and the Details tab of the Showcase Info section.</div><div>2. Wyrmsigils cannot be earned from summoning on a Platinum Showcase.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1664776800,update_time1649423560